      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Federal Deposit Insurance Act to require each insured depository institution which receives an investment or other assistance under the Troubled Assets Relief Program to include in the quarterly call report the amount of any increase in new lending that is attributable to such investment or assistance, and for other purposes.</title>
      </item>
